snippet.title: How to Craft Speeches by DTM Amber Wong
snippet.description:
Having trouble to craft your speeches? Want to connect with your audience faster and deeper? Watch this video!

DTM Amber Wong  shared her knowledge and experience on how to craft great speeches, the do's and don'ts, and what evaluator is looking in a speech.

Seeking to improve your public speaking skills? 
Join us at JB CITY TOASTMASTERS CLUB meeting to find out more!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jbcitytoastmasters/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jbcitytoastmasters/
